def classificationSvm(data):
    # Ucitavanje podataka
    df = pd.read_csv(data+'.csv')

    # Izvlacenje klasnog atributa
    labels = np.array(df['Class/ASD'])
    df = df.drop('Class/ASD', axis=1)
    df = np.array(df)

    # podela na trening itest skup
    train, test, train_labels, test_labels = train_test_split(df,
                                                              labels,
                                                              stratify=labels,
                                                              test_size=0.33,
                                                              random_state=0)

    # Random forest klasifikator, inicijalizacija
    model = SVC(kernel='linear')

    # Treniranje modela
    model.fit(train, train_labels)


    # Trening predikci

    # Test predikcija
    rf_predictions = model.predict(test)
    print(confusion_matrix(test_labels,rf_predictions))
    print(classification_report(test_labels,rf_predictions))


def classificationRF(data):
    df = pd.read_csv(data + '.csv')

    # Izvlacenje klasnog atributa
    labels = np.array(df['Class/ASD'])
    df = df.drop('Class/ASD', axis=1)
    df = np.array(df)

    # podela na trening itest skup
    train, test, train_labels, test_labels = train_test_split(df,
                                                              labels,
                                                              stratify=labels,
                                                              test_size=0.33,
                                                              random_state=0)

    # Random forest klasifikator, inicijalizacija
    model = RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=100,
                                   random_state=0,
                                   max_features='sqrt',
                                   n_jobs=-1, verbose=1)

    # Treniranje modela
    model.fit(train, train_labels)


    # Test predikcija
    rf_predictions = model.predict(test)
    print(confusion_matrix(test_labels,rf_predictions))
    print(classification_report(test_labels,rf_predictions))

from subprocess import call
from sklearn.tree import export_graphviz
from IPython.display import  Image

def tree(data):
    # Ucitavanje podataka
    dg = pd.read_csv(data + '.csv')

    # Izvlacenje klasnog atributa
    labels = np.array(dg['Class/ASD'])
    dg = dg.drop('Class/ASD', axis=1)
    df = np.array(dg)

    # podela na trening itest skup
    train, test, train_labels, test_labels = train_test_split(df,
                                                              labels,
                                                              stratify=labels,
                                                              test_size=0.33,
                                                              random_state=0)

    col = dg.columns.values

    # Random forest klasifikator, inicijalizacija
    model = RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=100,
                                   random_state=0,
                                   max_features='sqrt',
                                   n_jobs=-1, verbose=1)

    # Treniranje modela
    model.fit(train, train_labels)
    estimator = model.estimators_[5]

    # Eksport kao dot fajl
    export_graphviz(estimator, out_file=data + '.dot',
                    feature_names=col,
                    class_names='Class/ASD',
                    rounded=True, proportion=False,
                    precision=2, filled=True)

    call(['dot', '-Tpng', data + '.dot', '-o', data + '.png', '-Gdpi=600'])

    Image(filename=data+'.png')


def mainTree(data1):
    tree(data1)

mainTree('Podaci')

from sklearn.feature_selection import SelectKBest
from sklearn.feature_selection import f_classif
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier
from sklearn.feature_selection import RFE as RFEE
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np


def SelKBest(data, n):
    df = pd.read_csv(data+'.csv')

    # Izvlacenje klasnog atributa
    labels = df['Class/ASD']
    df = df.drop('Class/ASD', axis=1)
    cols = df.columns

    # feature extraction
    test = SelectKBest(score_func=f_classif, k=n)
    fit = test.fit(df, labels)
    # summarize scores
    np.set_printoptions(precision=3)
    # summarize selected features
    br = fit.get_support(indices=True)
    col = []
    for i in range(len(cols)):
        if i not in br:
            col.append(cols[i])
    print(br)
    df_new = df.drop(columns=col, axis=1)
    df_new = df_new.join(labels)

    df_new.to_csv('PPodaci.csv')


def RFE(data, n):
    df = pd.read_csv(data + '.csv')

    # Izvlacenje klasnog atributa
    labels = df['Class/ASD']
    df = df.drop('Class/ASD', axis=1)
    cols = df.columns
    # feature extraction
    model = RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=100)
    rfe = RFEE(model, n)
    fit = rfe.fit(df, labels)

    br = fit.get_support(indices=True)
    print(br)


RFE('Podaci', 1)
SelKBest('Podaci', 1)

import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.metrics import confusion_matrix
import vizualizacija as vs


def classification(data):
    # Ucitavanje podataka
    df = pd.read_csv(data+'.csv')

    # Izvlacenje klasnog atributa
    labels = np.array(df['Class/ASD'])
    df = df.drop('Class/ASD', axis=1)
    df = np.array(df)

    # podela na trening itest skup
    train, test, train_labels, test_labels = train_test_split(df,
                                                              labels,
                                                              stratify=labels,
                                                              test_size=0.33,
                                                              random_state=0)

    # Random forest klasifikator, inicijalizacija
    model = RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=100,
                                   random_state=0,
                                   max_features='sqrt',
                                   n_jobs=-1, verbose=1)

    # Treniranje modela
    model.fit(train, train_labels)

    n_cvorova = []
    max_dubina = []

    # Statistika
    for ind_tree in model.estimators_:
        n_cvorova.append(ind_tree.tree_.node_count)
        max_dubina.append(ind_tree.tree_.max_depth)

    print(f'Prosecan broj cvorova {int(np.mean(n_cvorova))}')
    print(f'Prosecna maksimalna dubina {int(np.mean(max_dubina))}')

    # Trening predikcija
    train_rf_predictions = model.predict(train)
    train_rf_probs = model.predict_proba(train)[:, 1]

    # Test predikcija
    rf_predictions = model.predict(test)
    rf_probs = model.predict_proba(test)[:, 1]

    # Grafikon
    plt.style.use('fivethirtyeight')
    plt.rcParams['font.size'] = 18



    vs.evaluate_model(rf_predictions, rf_probs, train_rf_predictions, train_rf_probs, test_labels, train_labels)

    cm = confusion_matrix(test_labels, rf_predictions)
    vs.plot_confusion_matrix(cm, classes=['Poor Health', 'Good Health'],
                          title='Health Confusion Matrix')

    plt.savefig(data+'Matrix.png')


def mainClassification(data1, data2):
    classification(data1)
    classification(data2)

mainClassification('Podaci','PPodaci')
